summary: New textures for males: dark, wood, and high elves, imperials, bretons, nords, and redguards.
descriptionHtml:
Since I like fantasy, I believe that elvels have to be handsome :) This is against TES Lore, but I just could not face with ugly elvels no more.

There are many fixes for female faces, so I decided to work on male faces a bit.

This mode changes faces of humans as well, but not so dramatically. It makes faces more clean and fresh. Check screenshots.

This mod will alter faces of NPC character as well, so be prepared :)
author: MikoYork

files.name: New textures for human and elven men
